msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/spellcasting/spells/chain_lightning.md:9
msgid "# Chain Lightning _6th-level evocation_"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/spellcasting/spells/chain_lightning.md:14
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**Casting Time:** 1 action    \n"
"**Range:** 150 feet    \n"
"**Components:** V, S, M (a bit of fur; a piece of amber, glass, or a crystal "
"rod; and three silver pins)    \n"
"**Duration:** Instantaneous \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/spellcasting/spells/chain_lightning.md:17
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"You create a bolt of lightning that arcs toward a target of your choice that "
"you can see within range. Three bolts then leap from that target to as many "
"as three other targets, each of which must be within 30 feet of the first "
"target. A target can be a creature or an object and can be targeted by only "
"one of the bolts.    \n"
"A target must make a Dexterity saving throw. The target takes 10d8 lightning "
"damage on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one. \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/spellcasting/spells/chain_lightning.md:18
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**At Higher Levels.** When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 7th "
"level or higher, one additional bolt leaps from the first target to another "
"target for each slot level above 6th. \n"
msgstr ""
